<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM8.4.5">
<l>ērār malarellā mūtinī yeṉpeṟuti</l>
<l>pārā rulakam paravap peruṅkaṭaluḷ</l>
<l>kārāmai yāṉakaṇ ṇapurat temperumāṉ</l>
<l>tārār naṟuntuḻāy tāḻntūtāy kōltumpī.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>What do you gain by sipping all of the beautiful flowers?</l>
<l>Twiggy dragonfly, alight and sip the fragrant tulasī that covers the garland</l>
<l>On our great lord of Kaṇṇapuram who became a dark turtle</l>
<l>In the wide sea when it extended [over] the land-covered earth.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
